Channel - Class in chanel
Channel,implemented in order to transmit values, from Generator, to Displayer Channel reprensents the Proxy in Active Object design pattern It had two roles: From Displayer to Generator , channel represents GeneratorAsyn that is a proxy of Generator; ie Displayer sees Channel as a Generator * From Generator to Displayer, channel represents Subject that get value
